2. **Tower/House Structure (Right):**
   - 7 blocks total
   - 4 layers
   - Bottom layer: Green cube and orange cube side by side
   - Second layer: Orange cube and green cube side by side (alternating pattern from first layer)
   - Third layer: Yellow cube and blue vertical rectangular block side by side
   - Top layer: Orange triangular roof piece on top

## Spatial Relationships:
- The vehicle's yellow rectangular block sits directly on top of the two cylindrical wheels
- The blue cube sits on the right end of the yellow rectangular block
- The tower structure has an alternating pattern of blocks, creating a colorful building
- The triangular roof sits atop the blue vertical rectangular block
